{"tid":2454133,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友開左一個社工群組 for 精神健康","createTime":"2021-03-20T04:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T10:50:43.000Z","uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10ba7698c0662fcf0bbb77b71f37461bb204e4b5","tid":2454133,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/nD9gjAuuywNhYTVl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FnD9gjAuuywNhYTVl&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=52a1894a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/nD9gjAuuywNhYTVl</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎讀psycho 或護理人士加入幫忙或揾研究材料。<br />\n<br />\n是這樣的， 社工係執行職務果陣唔可以暢所欲言，<br />\n咁所以就希望有一個有私隱嘅平台， 比社工， 醫護， 同病人，佢地去溝通， 可能係揾研究材料， 或者係幫病人。<br />\n<br />\n考慮到男義工對女性病人嘅可能性問題， 所以只建議男病人進入， 女性病人可考慮只參考或隱藏身份。"},{"pid":"5ec681f288a0733d9d1d258e7223dcebce89a0e7","tid":2454133,"uid":154373,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"好撚癲 當client 係增加工作經驗嘅study subject........"},{"pid":"7b4695a519c9dab6211b006b7cc610f3544b448d","tid":2454133,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"5ec681f288a0733d9d1d258e7223dcebce89a0e7","tid":2454133,"uid":154373,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"好撚癲 當client 係增加工作經驗嘅study subject........"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"你一路食住藥， 你去診所， 個醫生每次同你傾嘅<br />\n結果係加藥， 減藥定換藥。<br />\n<br />\n其他冇乜結論比到你，咁瘋唔瘋？<br />\n你去心理醫生， 好似同朋友傾計咁。<br />\n冇乜建樹， 咁瘋唔瘋。"},{"pid":"beca8a77ebdfcbd82bcf1c35acc8c79683b08301","tid":2454133,"uid":154373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7b4695a519c9dab6211b006b7cc610f3544b448d","tid":2454133,"uid":90323,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"5ec681f288a0733d9d1d258e7223dcebce89a0e7","tid":2454133,"uid":154373,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:25:09.000Z","msg":"好撚癲 當client 係